BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:0hm6u-JvBjeGD4Qm1xPBS
SUMMARY:Oral Peptides
DTSTAMP:20260322T022250Z
DTSTART:20260325T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Peptides are amino acids that work on proteins in your body\\\,
	 and are one of the hottest topics in healthcare right now. This talk with
	 Dr. Connie Amundsen provides answers to your questions about oral peptide
	s: how do they differ from injected peptides such as GLP-1 receptor agonis
	ts (Wegovy\\\, Ozempic)\\\, how do they work\\\, are they safe\\\, what co
	nditions are commonly treated\\\, are they affordable\\\, and how long doe
	s it take to see results? RSVP: 206.297.0875. \\nWednesday\\\, March 25\\\
	, 1-2pm. GSC. Free.\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/oral-peptides/\
	n\nFrom Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/oral-peptides/
LOCATION:Greenwood Senior Center\\\, 525 N. 85th St.\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\,
	 98103\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:phinney-neighborhood-association
CATEGORIES:Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
